==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
A primary verb

===Pronunciation===
βάλλω / ballō / bal'-lo

===Verb===
'''βάλλω'''

#to [[throw]] (in various applications, more or less violent or intense): - arise, cast (out), X dung, lay, lie, pour, put (up), send, strike, throw (down), thrust. 

